Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:05.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Both of them are stuck on this message
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.41,0:23:07.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and won't accept any commands at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:10.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's why we're having trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:13.72,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Raising Heart... Bardiche...\NAre they serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:18.12,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,CVK-792...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:22.98,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,A Belka-style Cartridge System...
